431
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:31,820
What do you need me to do? I said, everyone looked at me. For the first time all night. For the first

432
00:39:31,820 --> 00:39:37,520
time since he'd walked into the backstage hours before. I saw his expression crack. It was quick.

