439
00:40:12,420 --> 00:40:18,200
But between me and Evern, there was a bubble of a different silence. I saw something cross his face,

440
00:40:18,700 --> 00:40:24,200
something like shock, something like respect, something like a third thing I didn't have the vocabulary

441
00:40:24,200 --> 00:40:29,840
to name and decided not to try to name in that moment. All right, he said, you're way.

442
00:40:30,340 --> 00:40:36,040
Dario appeared at our side without making a sound. I hadn't even seen him move, and that detail alone

