451
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:29,200
one last time before leaving. He was standing leaned against the column. Hands in his jacket pockets.

452
00:41:29,760 --> 00:41:34,180
With the posture of someone waiting for the waiter to serve the second course. The jacket was

453
00:41:34,180 --> 00:41:38,980
Matt Black, and there was nothing in the position of his shoulders. In the tilt of his head.

