469
00:43:01,220 --> 00:43:06,900
and the sound rose along with me and I thought briefly about taking them off. Decided not to.

470
00:43:07,140 --> 00:43:12,080
That I would need to move fast eventually. And that running barefoot on an industrial floor was

471
00:43:12,080 --> 00:43:17,900
worse than running in heels. We reached the mezzanine. The hallway up there was narrower, with faded

472
00:43:17,900 --> 00:43:23,780
