473
00:43:24,080 --> 00:43:30,620
I knocked three times. The internal code the night crew used. Marcello opened. His eyes were wide and

474
00:43:30,620 --> 00:43:36,260
was a cup of coffee in his hand he'd forgotten to set down. Miss Cross. The hall. I know Marcello.

475
00:43:36,680 --> 00:43:42,400
Let me in. He stepped aside. Dario came in behind me and closed the door. The room was small.

476
00:43:42,800 --> 00:43:48,700
An entire wall of monitors showing every hallway, every exit, every floor of the hotel. Two

477
00:43:48,700 --> 00:43:53,420
consoles with keyboards worn from so much use. Three office chairs that had never been replaced.

478
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:58,400
It smelled a old coffee and plastic heated by the equipment. I went straight to the main

479
00:43:58,400 --> 00:44:03,180
console without taking my eyes off the monitors. My fingers knew the way from having entered

480
00:44:03,180 --> 00:44:08,140
that room so many times during events. I'm going to isolate the hall. I said,

