500
00:45:53,960 --> 00:45:58,980
the room and stayed inside. Back against the wall. Watching the hallway through the frosted glass.

501
00:45:59,440 --> 00:46:04,540
The room smelled of hot plastic and old coffee. Marcello's coffee, which he must have forgotten

