508
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:47,120
Whereas he, I asked, without taking my eyes off the screen. Dario didn't have to ask who I was talking

509
00:46:47,880 --> 00:46:54,380
about.  Ground  floor.  Behind  the  bar.  Alone?  He  preferred  it  that

510
00:46:54,380 --> 00:46:57,020
way.  I  pressed  the  next  button

