00:47:37,300 --> 00:47:43,120
And not yet worried. It was pure attention. The attention of someone trained not to waste movement.

520
00:47:43,680 --> 00:47:50,220
Are you going to ask me if I know what I'm doing? I said, no. Why not? Because he chose you.

521
00:47:50,500 --> 00:47:55,600
