531
00:48:42,780 --> 00:48:48,820
For you to finish. I raised my eyes to him. How long until I finish? Two minutes. You're good.

532
00:48:49,160 --> 00:48:54,800
I went back to the panel. I cut off the fourth floor. The fifth, the penthouse. I cut off

533
00:48:54,800 --> 00:48:59,980
